## Monitoring

DigitalOcean monitoring alerts are configured for:
- CPU usage > {{ cpu_alert_threshold }}% for 5 minutes
- Memory usage > {{ memory_alert_threshold }}% for 5 minutes
- Disk usage > {{ disk_alert_threshold }}% for 5 minutes
- Load average > 2× vCPUs for 5 minutes

Alerts are sent to: `{{ alert_email }}`
